ip access-list standard 1
 remark INTERNAL-SERVER-SUBNET
 permit 92.33.56.32 0.0.0.31
 deny any
!
no snmp-server community public RO
no snmp-server community private RW
logging trap notifications
!
!
snmp-server location Glitched
snmp-server contact noc@infra.glitched.se
snmp-server system-shutdown
snmp-server community GLITCHED-RO RO 1
snmp-server enable traps snmp linkdown linkup coldstart warmstart
snmp-server enable traps snmp authentication
snmp-server enable traps config
snmp-server view gwrite iso included
snmp-server view gread iso included
snmp-server ifindex persist
